{"id":2,"idInBook":1263,"chapterId":54,"bookId":15,"arabic":"حَدَّثَنَا الأُوَيْسِيُّ، قَالَ‏:‏ حَدَّثَنَا سُلَيْمَانُ بْنُ بِلاَلٍ، عَنْ مُوسَى بْنِ عُقْبَةَ، عَنْ نَافِعٍ، عَنِ ابْنِ عُمَرَ قَالَ‏:‏ الْمَيْسِرُ‏:‏ الْقِمَارُ‏.‏","english":{"narrator":"","text":"Ibn 'Umar said, \"Arrow-shuffling is gambling.\""},"hadithNumber":1263,"hadithId":2,"reference":"54:2","meta":{"id":"aladab_almufrad","length":1326,"totalChapters":57,"arabic":{"title":"الأدب المفرد","author":"الإمام محمد بن إسماعيل البخاري"},"english":{"title":"Al-Adab Al-Mufrad","author":"Imam Muhammad ibn Ismail al-Bukhari"}},"chapter":{"id":54,"bookId":15,"arabic":"كتاب القمار ونحوه","english":"Betting and similar pastimes","startHadith":1262,"endHadith":1284,"totalHadiths":23},"version":{"name":"aladab_almufrad","title":"Al-Adab Al-Mufrad","chapters":57}}